      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LINDENOW BUFFY (6) was well fancied but drifted back before winding up with a late dash home to place, 6 lengths from the winner (26.46) at this track in T3 RSTW. Can find winning form. MEMPHIS MACK (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (23.57) in a Grade 5 at this track. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Can measure up this time. BLUE TROMBONE (4) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at Bendigo over 425m behind Sheikh Of Tweak (25.15) in a Rank Limit - Grade 6. Cannot be underestimated. BERNARDO SPLIT (1) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
